{
  "stem": "26792.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said [SPEAKING GERMAN POORLY] He did this and he left me alone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The moment he went back to the room, I opened the front door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very cold winter day in February in Riga.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I left the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went along the street without a coat, without a hat, in a dress.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People-- Latvian people, Christian people, were coming from church.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody paid any attention to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody asked me who I was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then it occurred to me that Mrs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Steinbach, ?] a friend of mine, was hiding-- had been hiding in the place of a Dutchman, which was not too far away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I knocked on his door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He never seen me before and I said, the Gestapo is in my house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They're going to arrest me if you don't let me in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm a friend of Mrs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Steinbach. ?] And he opened the door and he let me in-- a very cultured, very intelligent man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then he found Ianis for me in the evening and--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe hours, hours only.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The same day, same evening, he picked me up and we went back to that house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Richard van Ham.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "R-I-C-H-A-R-D, now comes a small V-A-N capital H-A-M.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the first place, I heard from Lidums and Kraujinsh that a street where my parents, where I had lived before, across a Jewish old cemetery, that all the inhabitants had already been killed in the Rumbula, that is on the 8th of December.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It means my family was not there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, uh, secondly-- and secondly, I was in touch with the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So where I lived in Miera iela, my nanny was with us constantly.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
